## Model architecture
- GNN: GraphSAGE, 3 layers, 128→512→512
- Prompt encoder: frozen PubMedBERT (microsoft/BiomedNLP-PubMedBERT), CLS pooling → 768-dim
- Conditioning: FiLM (γ,β = MLP(prompt); h' = γ⊙h + β)
- Predictor: concat(gene_emb, disease_emb) → MLP → score
- Training: BCE + ranking + listnet loss, 5 negatives per positive

