## Paper framing
- Lead metric: Hit Rate@50 (0.5573) — clinically meaningful, easy to explain
- Headline metric: AUROC (0.9626) — good for abstract
- Do NOT lead with AUPR in paper — low value is expected, not a flaw
- Paper story: FiLM-conditioned GraphSAGE outperforms static-feature baselines
  for rare disease gene prioritization, with zero-shot generalization
- Zero-shot set: 117 diseases with ≤5 known genes, confirmed not in training split

